- Yeah.

1025
01:09:47,240 --> 01:09:50,676
l don't want her to grow up alone.
lt's not good to grow up alone.

1026
01:09:50,800 --> 01:09:54,076
- She'll be too lonely.
- That's wonderful.

1027
01:10:43,800 --> 01:10:45,756
(horse neighs)

1028
01:10:52,800 --> 01:10:55,837
(Kleinman) lrmy, look out!
Look out! lt's the killer!

1029
01:10:55,960 --> 01:10:58,838
- Kleinman!
- Yes, l'm here! Run! Run! Run!

1030
01:10:58,960 --> 01:11:02,236
- What about you?
- Don't worry. l'll take care of...

1031
01:11:02,360 --> 01:11:05,432
- Don't come near her. Run! Run!
- What about you?

1032
01:11:05,560 --> 01:11:08,199
Don't worry about me.
l can take care of myself.

1033
01:11:08,320 --> 01:11:10,276
Don't come near me.

1034
01:11:22,280 --> 01:11:24,236
(man groans)

1035
01:11:35,840 --> 01:11:40,197
Good evening.
l am Almstead the magician.

1036
01:11:41,240 --> 01:11:44,277
Almstead! My God!
l do some tricks myself.

1037
01:11:44,400 --> 01:11:47,312
l'm an amateur magician.
You're my idol. l came to see you.

1038
01:11:47,440 --> 01:11:50,238
l was just celebrating
our closing performance.

1039
01:11:50,360 --> 01:11:54,876
And also, of course, packing up
my illusions and my paraphernalia.

1040
01:11:55,000 --> 01:11:58,834
The killer's loose.
You have to stop. The killer is loose.

1041
01:11:58,960 --> 01:12:01,520
- The evil one.
- Yes! Yes. Roaming...

1042
01:12:02,360 --> 01:12:05,318
There he is!
Think of something! Think quick!

1043
01:12:06,400 --> 01:12:08,834
Come! Come! Over here!

1044
01:12:08,960 --> 01:12:11,349
