1045
01:12:11,480 --> 01:12:14,836
My mirror illusion.
Come! You must help. Come!

1046
01:12:16,600 --> 01:12:18,556
Yes! Come!

1047
01:12:22,120 --> 01:12:25,430
Come. Come, young man.
Come. Jump into the mirror.

1048
01:12:25,560 --> 01:12:28,358
Come. The evil one comes.

1049
01:12:28,480 --> 01:12:30,436
Just jump. Jump!

1050
01:12:31,360 --> 01:12:32,475
