1052
01:13:35,880 --> 01:13:38,474
Yes, we got him. We got him!

1053
01:13:38,600 --> 01:13:42,957
- lt's fantastic. He was right...
- Yes, he was here. Now he's there.

1054
01:13:43,080 --> 01:13:47,358
- (lrmy) Come on, everybody! He's in here!
- (Kleinman) We got him.

1055
01:13:47,480 --> 01:13:51,109
- Where is he?
- He is over there, bound in chains.

1056
01:13:51,240 --> 01:13:55,028
- Where is he?
- Over there. Bound hand and foot in ch...

