1059
01:14:01,880 --> 01:14:05,395
- Kleinman saw him. He was here.
- l did. He was right over here.

1060
01:14:05,520 --> 01:14:08,318
No man could have escaped from...

1061
01:14:08,440 --> 01:14:11,910
Look! Look, you see.
Here. These are the real locks.

1062
01:14:12,040 --> 01:14:14,156
Almstead, you drink too much.

1063
01:14:14,280 --> 01:14:17,272
