1069
01:14:36,680 --> 01:14:40,355
All l know is you certainly saved my life.
You were very brave.

1070
01:14:40,480 --> 01:14:43,995
Well, l can be brave.
lt's just that l can't think about it first.

1071
01:14:44,120 --> 01:14:49,274
lf l ever think about what's gonna happen
to me, then l lose control of my muscles.

1072
01:14:50,240 --> 01:14:52,879
Well, l guess this is goodbye.

1073
01:14:53,000 --> 01:14:55,639
We're gonna be pulling out in a few hours.

1074
01:14:55,760 --> 01:14:58,069
lt's been a strange night, hasn't it?

1075
01:14:58,200 --> 01:15:00,430
l feel like my whole life has changed.

1076
01:15:00,560 --> 01:15:02,994
Me too. Very unusual.

1077
01:15:03,960 --> 01:15:05,712
So are you gonna be OK?

1078
01:15:05,840 --> 01:15:10,834
