1099
01:16:20,600 --> 01:16:23,353
You know. What kind of question is that?

1100
01:16:23,480 --> 01:16:26,313
l could marry my landlady
and run a boarding house.

1101
01:16:26,440 --> 01:16:29,193
Yes, yes, yes. The grey hat.

1102
01:16:29,320 --> 01:16:33,438
Sooner or later we all must put on
the grey hat of compromise.

1103
01:16:33,560 --> 01:16:35,312
No, l'm, you know...

1104
01:16:35,440 --> 01:16:39,638
