1113
01:17:08,360 --> 01:17:12,319
Although, l must say, to be
Almstead's assistant would be...

1114
01:17:14,400 --> 01:17:17,278
lt's crazy. lt's just a dream.

1115
01:17:17,400 --> 01:17:21,757
Well, l don't know if we're gonna be
passing through this way again.

1116
01:17:26,680 --> 01:17:28,989
- Good luck.
- You take care of yourself.

1117
01:17:29,120 --> 01:17:31,076
- You too.
