1131
01:18:35,200 --> 01:18:37,760
What better way to spend
the rest of my life...

1132
01:18:37,880 --> 01:18:41,077
..than to help you with all those
wonderful illusions of yours?

1133
01:18:41,200 --> 01:18:43,839
